videos.headline: McNichols goes 83 yards for first-play TD
videos.description: On the first play from scrimmage, Boise State's Jeremy McNichols goes up the middle untouched for the 83-yard touchdown to put the Broncos up 7-0.

videos.headline: AFA vs. BSU
Air Force trickery goes for 67-yard TD
videos.description: Air Force rolled out to run the option, but instead, Karson Roberts throws the ball downfield to Jalen Robinette, who goes the rest of the way for a 67-yard touchdown putting the Falcons up 17-13.

videos.headline: AFA vs. BSU
McVey sweeps all the way into the end zone
videos.description: Air Force's Timothy McVey takes the pitch sweep and goes untouched 48 yards to the end zone to extend the Falcons' lead to 24-13.

videos.headline: Air Force strikes again with long TD pass
videos.description: Air Force keeps the big-play offense rolling with a 51-yard touchdown pass to a wide open Garrett Griffin for the score.
